      <title>Laravel</title>
      <link href="/2018/05/13/WeekLaravel/"/>
      <url>/2018/05/13/WeekLaravel/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>摸鱼踩坑<br><a id="more"></a></p><h1 id="第一周笔记"><a href="#第一周笔记" class="headerlink" title="第一周笔记"></a>第一周笔记</h1><h3 id="目录"><a href="#目录" class="headerlink" title="目录"></a>目录</h3><p><img src="http://p3qiw6uhk.bkt.clouddn.com/TIM%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20180513093406.png" alt="目录"><br>app:核心代码。包含了站点的controllers（控制器），models（模型），views（视图）和assets（资源）。<br>bootstrap：框架启动自动加载配置<br>config：所有应用程序配置<br>database：数据库迁移与填充文件<br>public：入口和项目文件。这个文件夹是唯一外界可以看到的，必须指向web服务器的目录。它含有laravel框架核心的引导文件index.php，这个目录也可用来存放任何可以公开的静态资源，如css，Javascript，images等。<br>resources：视图和原始的资源文件，其中的views就是MVC中的V层。<br>storage：编译后的模板文件以及基于文件的session文件缓存、日志和其他框架产生的缓存<br>tests：单元测试文件<br>vendor：用来存放所有的第三方代码，在一个典型的Laravel应用程序，这包括Laravel源代码及其相关，并含有额外的预包装功能的插件。<br><a href="https://laravel-china.org/docs/laravel/5.5/structure/1284" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Laravel 的文件夹结构</a></p><h3 id="路由"><a href="#路由" class="headerlink" title="路由"></a>路由</h3><h4 id="基本路由"><a href="#基本路由" class="headerlink" title="基本路由"></a>基本路由</h4><p>实现了下基本路由，Laravel框架下的第一个Hello world！<br><code>routes/web.php</code><br><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Route::get(<span class="string">'HelloWorld'</span>,<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">'Hello world!'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><img src="http://p3qiw6uhk.bkt.clouddn.com/TIM%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20180513202222.png" alt="HelloWorld"></p><h4 id="路由方法"><a href="#路由方法" class="headerlink" title="路由方法"></a>路由方法</h4><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Route::get($uri, $callback);</span><br><span class="line">Route::post($uri, $callback);</span><br><span class="line">Route::put($uri, $callback);</span><br><span class="line">Route::patch($uri, $callback);</span><br><span class="line">Route::delete($uri, $callback);</span><br><span class="line">Route::options($uri, $callback);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="多请求路由"><a href="#多请求路由" class="headerlink" title="多请求路由"></a>多请求路由</h4><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">match指定方法，any响应所有。</span><br><span class="line">Route::match([<span class="string">'方法'</span>],<span class="string">'路由名'</span>,<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">Route::any(<span class="string">'路由名'</span>,<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="路由参数"><a href="#路由参数" class="headerlink" title="路由参数"></a>路由参数</h4><p>在路由中捕获一些URL片段。参数通常都会被放在<code>{}</code>内，参数名只能为字母，同时路由参数不能包含<code>-</code>，如果需要可以用下划线 <code>_</code>代替。路由参数会按顺序依次被注入到路由回调或者控制器中，而不受回调或者控制器的参数名称的影响。</p><h5 id="必填参数"><a href="#必填参数" class="headerlink" title="必填参数"></a>必填参数</h5><p>单个参数<br><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Route::get(<span class="string">'&#123;id&#125;'</span>,<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">($id)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">'大家好我是钾盐哇×'</span>.$id;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><img src="http://p3qiw6uhk.bkt.clouddn.com/3.png" alt="单个参数"><br>多个参数<br><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Route::get(<span class="string">'catagory/&#123;catagoryid&#125;/article/&#123;articleid&#125;'</span>,<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">($catagoryid,$articleid)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">'分类ID：'</span>.$catagoryid.<span class="string">'  '</span>.<span class="string">'文章ID:'</span>.$articleid;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><img src="http://p3qiw6uhk.bkt.clouddn.com/4.png" alt="多个参数"></p><h5 id="可选参数"><a href="#可选参数" class="headerlink" title="可选参数"></a>可选参数</h5><p>指定一个路由参数，这个参数是可选的。在参数后面加上<code>?</code>来实现,但前提确保路由的相应变量有默认值<br><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Route::get(<span class="string">'name/&#123;name?&#125;'</span>,<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">($name=<span class="string">'KCL'</span>)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">'My name is:'</span>.$name;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><img src="http://p3qiw6uhk.bkt.clouddn.com/5.png" alt="可选参数"></p><h5 id="正则表达式约束"><a href="#正则表达式约束" class="headerlink" title="正则表达式约束"></a>正则表达式约束</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Route::get(<span class="string">'name/&#123;name&#125;/id/&#123;id&#125;'</span>,<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">($name,$id)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">'user-'</span>.$name.<span class="string">'-'</span>.<span class="string">'id-'</span>.$id;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)-&gt;where([<span class="string">'name'</span>=&gt;<span class="string">'[A-Za-z]+'</span>,<span class="string">'id'</span>=&gt;<span class="string">'[0-9]+'</span>]);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="http://p3qiw6uhk.bkt.clouddn.com/6.png" alt="正则表达式"></p><h4 id="路由别名"><a href="#路由别名" class="headerlink" title="路由别名"></a>路由别名</h4><h4 id="路由群组"><a href="#路由群组" class="headerlink" title="路由群组"></a>路由群组</h4><p><a href="https://laravel-china.org/docs/laravel/5.5/routing/1293" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Laravel HTTP 路由功能</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Laravel </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
